{"id":155,"ayahs":[{"number":38,"arabic":"قَالَ ٱدْخُلُوا۟ فِىٓ أُمَمٍۢ قَدْ خَلَتْ مِن قَبْلِكُم مِّنَ ٱلْجِنِّ وَٱلْإِنسِ فِى ٱلنَّارِ ۖ كُلَّمَا دَخَلَتْ أُمَّةٌۭ لَّعَنَتْ أُخْتَهَا ۖ حَتَّىٰٓ إِذَا ٱدَّارَكُوا۟ فِيهَا جَمِيعًۭا قَالَتْ أُخْرَىٰهُمْ لِأُولَىٰهُمْ رَبَّنَا هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ أَضَلُّونَا فَـَٔاتِهِمْ عَذَابًۭا ضِعْفًۭا مِّنَ ٱلنَّارِ ۖ قَالَ لِكُلٍّۢ ضِعْفٌۭ وَلَٰكِن لَّا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"[And God] will say: \"Join those hosts of invisible beings and humans who have gone before you into the fire!\" [And] every time a host enters [the fire], it will curse its fellow-host -so much so that, when they all shall have passed into it, one after another, the last of them will speak [thus] of the first of them: \"O our Sustainer! It is they who have led us astray: give, them, therefore, double suffering through fire!\" He, will reply: \"Every one of you deserves double suffering -but you know it not.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/992.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":40252,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(আল্লাহ) বলবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40253,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱدْخُلُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা প্রবেশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40254,"position":3,"arabic":"فِىٓ","translation":"সাথে (অন্তর্ভুক্ত হয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40255,"position":4,"arabic":"أُمَمٍۢ","translation":"জাতিগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40256,"position":5,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40257,"position":6,"arabic":"خَلَتْ","translation":"গত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40258,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40259,"position":8,"arabic":"قَبْلِكُم","translation":"পূর্ব তোমাদের","audi